latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Eversince we are in relationship, I oftenly ask you to sing me a song, sometimes you refused and sometimes you sung songs with your own customised lyrics.

But today you sung whole song with accurate lyrics and that too with a guitar which you learnt for me in few weeks... @drumsonboard_mayank I just want to tell you this is best gift i have recevied from you till date ♥️ I am blessed to have you in my life and I LOVE YOU babie♥️
